├── tests/
│   ├── test_dbus_client.py
│   ├── test_animations.py
│   └── test_pam_auth.py
└── README.md
```

**System Integration Tasks:**
1. Create systemd user service for auto-start
2. Register D-Bus service for lock/unlock commands
3. Add GNOME keyboard shortcut for manual lock
4. Handle suspend/resume events (lock on lid close)
5. Multi-monitor wallpaper blur
6. Graceful fallback if sensor disconnected

